data.description: You will love this beautiful home! Well maintained 3 bedrooms with 2 full baths. The living room has cathedral ceilings with an open concept. The kitchen is nice and has enough space for all your Holiday cooking and all appliances stay! Big fenced in back yard for the kids and pets. Also has a beautiful deck for entertainment. This home is in a wonderful neighborhood and is minutes away from shopping and the interstate.
